              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="feature">
                <i class="feature-icon"><img src="assets/experiment.png" alt=""></i>
                <h2 class="feature-title">Practical hub</h2>
                <p>Assumenda est, omnis dolor repellendus. Temporibus autem quibusdam et aut officiis debitis aut rerum necessitatibus saepe eveniet voluptates.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <div class="feature">
                <i class="feature-icon"><img src="assets/about-us.png" alt=""></i>
                <h2 class="feature-title">About US</h2>
                <p>Praesentium voluptatum deleniti atque corrupti quos dolores et quas molestias excepturi sint occaecati cupiditate non provident similique.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </main> <!-- .main-content -->
     </div>
   <% end %>

     <!-- .main-content -->
